        <mxCell id="KTXAC8cRg_mJXfXTqlD4-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=15;" value="X1: Early Client creation is causing clutter in XPM - XPM for managed work not for Transactions, this affect no only on client master, but also on the IC data, where it has to be excluded from any reporting to get the correct figures&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;X2: this way create a retro action, all the work related is done and doesn&#39;t serve any purpose, unnecessary admin work&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;X3: the entire onboarding is not tracked or visible in 1 place, all components require manual work, clear inefficency.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;X4: an external process not integrated with the onboarding process.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;X5: big inefficency, more risk of miss, duplication and create unnecassary admin work - small enhancement can kill this broken process&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;X6: Karbon introduced in later stage, not connected to the process, and not doing the basic tracking features.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
